@database DCTV_Retina.library
@author Chris Gerrist
@(C) 1994 by C Gerrist

@node main 
    The DCTV.library is a library for the Retina Graphic board.
    © 1994 by C Gerrist, Holland.


    This library is shareware.

    I have made this library so Imagine can render direct on a
    24 bit window on the Retina Board. 
    This is the unregistered demo version. It displays 3 pictures
    in the displayed picture. If you registrate you get the full
    version.

    @{"    index    " link index}
@endnode

